      <title>中国收益率曲线趋陡贸易获得关注，但存在警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-yield-curve-steepener-trade-gains-traction-with-caveats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种流行的国债交易正在中国得到复制，随着央行努力更好地控制债券市场并发出更健康的经济信号，长期和短期收益率之间的差距正在扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-yield-curve-steepener-trade-gains-traction-with-caveats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
