      <title>加拿大央行因消费者支出减少而改变态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bank-of-canada-changes-tune-as-consumers-show-they-re-hurting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆非常有信心央行已经抑制了通货膨胀，因此他调整了央行的决策程序——官员们现在正在设定利率，以防止价格压力放缓过多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bank-of-canada-changes-tune-as-consumers-show-they-re-hurting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
